Class AdaptiveSharingAnalyser

  • java.lang.Object
    • AdaptiveSharingAnalyser

  • public class AdaptiveSharingAnalyser
extends Object
    this class takes as input parameters: 1. learned re-share probabilities for different sensitive levels, e.g., [] learntProbs, 2. the associated reward r3 (see DTMC diagram) 3. the infoType which stipulates the actual sensitivity level associated with the item of information that user wants to share.
